  "title": "🦅❤️‍🔥 COMMERCIAL SALES CONSULTANT – High Income & Career Growth 🚀",
  "description": "<p>📍 <strong>Location:</strong> Boat Quay<br>\n🏢 <strong>Company:</strong> Euphoria Organization<br>\n🕒 <strong>Full-Time</strong> | 💼 <strong>Immediate Start</strong></p>\n<h3><strong>✨ What You’ll Do</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>🤝 Engage in <strong>B2B &amp; B2C sales</strong> at events, roadshows, and face-to-face meetings</li>\n  <li>💼 Build &amp; maintain strong <strong>client relationships</strong></li>\n  <li>📈 Achieve <strong>sales targets</strong> &amp; contribute to <strong>business growth</strong></li>\n  <li>🎯 Match <strong>products &amp; solutions</strong> to customer needs</li>\n  <li>🌏 Represent <strong>top MNC brands</strong> locally &amp; regionally</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>💎 What You Get</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>💰 <strong>Uncapped commissions</strong> + bonuses</li>\n  <li>🛫 <strong>Travel opportunities</strong> (regional &amp; overseas)</li>\n  <li>🧠 <strong>1-to-1 mentorship</strong> &amp; structured training</li>\n  <li>📊 Transparent <strong>career progression</strong> (Sales → Leadership → Management)</li>\n  <li>🎉 Energetic, supportive &amp; fun team</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>✅ Who We’re Looking For</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>🌟 Positive, motivated &amp; adaptable</li>\n  <li>🗣 Strong communication &amp; people skills</li>\n  <li>🎓 <strong>No experience needed</strong> – full training provided</li>\n  <li>🇸🇬 <strong>Singaporeans &amp; PRs only</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>📩 <strong>APPLY NOW</strong> – Build your sales career with Euphoria Organization and grow without limits!</p>",
